83,"uid":81113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1693da285f7bf4895233ec4915371ace8a750824","tid":799683,"uid":19527,"like":203,"dislike":1,"score":202,"citedBy":6,"replyTime":"2018-08-30T11:12:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/30/191232_b68c482c4cc1ef894367fbcccf20d1e3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F30%2F191232_b68c482c4cc1ef894367fbcccf20d1e3.png&h=99b511c1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n樓上個黑人唔關事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-30T13:37:40.000Z","msg":"都ok喎"},{"pid":"fb81a9a5650c575c40a7d9b1f0666d8623c80cb4","tid":799683,"uid":138736,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"5f2ea6a80040e7565c1215a651c11724751b7371","tid":799683,"uid":24160,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"bf768643135f38a65cb3dcd8c474711fa7b39ff9","tid":799683,"uid":138736,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-30T11:12:28.000Z","msg":"叫親 Elizabeth 都係淫娃"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-30T13:35:52.000Z","msg":"汪明荃?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-30T13:37:46.000Z","msg":"人地叫Lisa<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nbtw elizabeth olsen<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef2fc2210fe234076e919eb94750520aaaf41d3d","tid":799683,"uid":24160,"like":3,"dislike":21,"score":-18,"quote":{"pid":"fb81a9a5650c575c40a7d9b1f0666d8623c80cb4","tid":799683,"uid":138736,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"5f2ea6a80040e7565c1215a651c11724751b7371","tid":799683,"uid":24160,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"bf768643135f38a65cb3dcd8c474711fa7b39ff9","tid":799683,"uid":138736,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-30T11:12:28.000Z","msg":"叫親 Elizabeth 都係淫娃"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-30T13:35:52.000Z","msg":"汪明荃?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-30T13:37:46.000Z","msg":"人地叫Lisa<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nbtw elizabeth olsen<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-30T13:39:16.000Z","msg":"mark 大你個屎眼睇清楚<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://photouploads.com/images/776df7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fphotouploads.com%2Fimages%2F776df7.jpg&h=3ccbb8ac&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">No!!!剛好相反!!!「退休？冇諗過。除非冇人再想睇我。」</span></span><br />\n<br />\n明年將踏入半世紀演藝生涯的汪明荃（阿蛆），認為七十歲就已是「古來稀」。堅毅不屈的阿蛆表示沒有想過退休，因為牠直言不懼怕年老，儘管擔心麻煩別既照顧，但只要身體沒什麼毛病就可以繼續行下去。過往見證著一個又一個老友離㸱而去，牠更明白一個道理：想做什麼便去做，一日未死，也要繼續去做。<br />\n<br />\n見到阿蛆對「年老」有一套堅毅、樂觀同積極既睇法，就不得不回顧牠約二十歲入行時的心境。「當時18歲係有一道everlasting 既火，而家唔可以再留戀，唯一可以做既，就係要不斷push up自己！」<br />\n難怪環顧整個娛樂點圈，有阿蛆咁豐富既資歷真係十分稀有。再者，阿蛆既自強不息、堅毅積極既精神，使牠喺不論歌藝生涯，定係外在方面都一樣不斷進步。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://photouploads.com/images/ccab77.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fphotouploads.com%2Fimages%2Fccab77.jpg&h=f33769ed&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://photouploads.com/images/a08c6e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fphotouploads.com%2Fimages%2Fa08c6e.jpg&h=34c73c3d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://photouploads.com/images/13cdc7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fphotouploads.com%2Fimages%2F13cdc7.jpg&h=dc566827&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://photouploads.com/images/79632c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fphotouploads.com%2Fimages%2F79632c.jpg&h=70e01bc5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://photouploads.com/images/43596e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fphotouploads.com%2Fimages%2F43596e.jpg&h=325e3129&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n&sect;不屈不撓的阿蛆於㕑房地磚下仍然高聲歌唱<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://youtu.be/vsgkml5zRqI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fvsgkml5zRqI&d=WSR0BhHqB%2BG9nNySSTDKzp4f2li5K%2Fs6EGgmwhpeblA%3D&h=35c52807\" target=\"_blank\">http://youtu.be/vsgkml5zRqI</a><br />\nKTV版<br />\n<a href=\"http://youtu.be/LqOVt820k78\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FLqOVt820k78&d=WSR0BhHqB%2BG9nNySSTDKzp4f2li5K%2Fs6EGgmwhpeblA%3D&h=08d66d0d\" target=\"_blank\">http://youtu.be/LqOVt820k78</a><br />\n<img src=\"http://photouploads.com/images/9e80ad.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fphotouploads.com%2Fimages%2F9e80ad.jpg&h=4b2ce457&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n&sect; 力求進步阿蛆亦不斷擴濶自己既高音域，以特殊共鳴部位發聲的技巧、巧奪天工的天籟唱腔，不但穩固咗阿蛆近半世紀於樂壇殿堂級之江山地位，更將自己的唱藝事業邁向另一高峰！"},{"pid":"ddc7679b85e571768992fbd2aa98344c71c3ee85","tid":799683,"uid":13308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1693da285f7bf4895233ec4915371ace8a750824","tid":799683,"uid":19527,"like":203,"dislike":1,"score":202,"citedBy":6,"replyTime":"2018-08-30T11:12:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/30/191232_b68c482c4cc1ef894367fbcccf20d1e3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F30%2F191232_b68c482c4cc1ef894367fbcccf20d1e3.png&h=99b511c1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n樓上個黑人唔關事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-30T13:40:59.000Z","msg":"要搞就搞我<br />\n唔姐連累d細既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2efa844dc8a935f8675d2ebfb53bf02574962031","tid":799683,"uid":138736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-30T13:41:16.000Z","msg":"wfc <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"26113fe9aa4854fb3b2f87a00c479efc59595776","tid":799683,"uid":30801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-30T13:48:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/